pageContext.claim: “House Democrats, fresh off a Republican victory against them (in Federal Court) on the Wall,  keep asking people to come and testify regarding the No Collusion Witch Hunt. They are very unhappy with the Mueller Report, especially with his corrective letter, & now want a Do Over!”
pageContext.analysis: Another case against Trump's wall funding is proceeding forward. Special counsel Robert Mueller's statement was damaging to Trump and energized efforts to launch impeachment proceedings.
